  "non_oss_deps": null,
  "anticipated_spec_changes": "In https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/9452 there was consideration of passing an element to contain the scroll to. As discussed in https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/9452#issuecomment-2607879021 we think this is easily added in a backwards compatible way if there is a need for it.",
